reviews.text:
Food is great.  Service is fair.  Tables are unreasonably tightly placed otherwise it can earn a 5-star rating for its relatively cheap price and yet superb food.  Not a pleasant experience to lunch here at peak hours.  Soy sauce shrimp is a must try.  Got this dish 3 times here, all so so satisfying despite the environment.

(Updated on 2019-04-06)
4 times now!  Arrived shortly after they opened at 11:30am on a Saturday, so much better when fewer diners were there.
Served good and nice authentic Korean foods at reasonable price.
despite of the sqeezy seating, food are so delicious  😋
I expected a bit more of beef and the egg would be bigger. Taste not bad!
Great Kimchi pajeon(pancake) and bulgogi

result.formatted_address: 號地下, 53 Pilkem St, Jordan, 香港
result.name: Jang Dok Korean Restaurant

reviews.text: 光顧了兩次:第一次與朋友坐了很久，傾得暢快;但第二次卻被職員話你吃完就要走，外面有人等，很不客氣，沒禮貌。兩次只是相隔一星期，也是二人光顧，亦是平日。這種服務態度不要得，又沒交代只可吃1小時/1.5小時/2小時，好吃韓式料理有很多，永遠也不光顧。

Food is great.  Service is fair.  Tables are unreasonably tightly placed otherwise it can earn a 5-star rating for its relatively cheap price and yet superb food.  Not a pleasant experience to lunch here at peak hours.  Soy sauce shrimp is a must try.  Got this dish 3 times here, all so so satisfying despite the environment.

(Updated on 2019-04-06)
4 times now!  Arrived shortly after they opened at 11:30am on a Saturday, so much better when fewer diners were there.
無預期中咁好味，煎而非燒的五花腩，偏硬略韌，豆腐湯味道唔夠濃，但價錢唔貴，仍然值四粒星。
醬油蟹超好味，咁多年都無失水準
Served good and nice authentic Korean foods at reasonable price.
